data.description: Creekside feel without the HOA! Large lot in great neighborhood and stunning backyard views! Granite counters in the kitchen with an abundance of storage and SS appliances. Gas fireplace in family room. All bedrooms are upstairs, leaving downstairs with large, open gathering spaces. Primary has great views as well as soaking tub and tile in bath. Large, fenced backyard with shed, deck and RV parking space next to house. Assumable VA loan available for qualified veterans 3.125% interest rate!
